 延迟零代码改动</title><link>https://claudeai.best/posts/hunter-2026021919/</link><pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 19:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://claudeai.best/posts/hunter-2026021919/</guid><description>Aegis.rs 是首个开源 Rust LLM 安全代理,透明拦截请求,150+ 启发式规则 + AI 审判,零代码改动,本地运行,1ms 延迟.</description></item><item><title>Martin Fowler:LLM正在吞噬专业技能,专家型通才的时代来了</title><link>https://claudeai.best/posts/hunter-2026021901/</link><pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://claudeai.best/posts/hunter-2026021901/</guid><description>Thoughtworks软件未来大会核心洞察:LLM正在替代前后端专家技能,TDD成为最强的prompt engineering,AI是加速器而非救世主--如果你的工程实践一团糟,AI只会加速崩溃.</description></item><item><title>Claude Sonnet 4.6发布:性能对标Opus,价格不变,还学会了用电脑</title><link>https://claudeai.best/posts/hunter-2026021820/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Feb 2026 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://claudeai.best/posts/hunter-2026021820/</guid><description>Anthropic今天发布Claude Sonnet 4.6,性能接近去年11月的Opus 4.5,但价格保持在$3/$15每百万token.最亮眼的是电脑操作能力--在OSWorld基准测试中,16个月内从3.6%飙升至接近人类水平.开发者测试中70%的人更喜欢它而不是前代产品.</description></item><item><title>NVIDIA PersonaPlex-7B:一个7B模型把整个语音AI行业打回原形</title><link>https://claudeai.best/posts/hunter-2026021819/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Feb 2026 19:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://claudeai.best/posts/hunter-2026021819/</guid><description>NVIDIA开源7B参数全双工语音模型PersonaPlex,将ASR+LLM+TTS三合一,170毫秒延迟击败所有商业API.语音AI的利润正在从API层向GPU层迁移,这个行业的天又变了.</description></item></channel></rss>